PROJECT.NAME: qcLitStyg1-mito
PROJECT.TITLE: Lithobius stygius, mitochondrial assembly, qcLitStyg1-mito.
PROJECT.DESCRIPTION: This project provides a mitochondrial assembly of Lithobius stygius. The assembly is provided by the European Reference Genome Atlas (ERGA, https://www.erga-biodiversity.eu/) via the Biodiversity Genomics Europe project (BGE, https://biodiversitygenomics.eu/).
